Apple Music Pop

Updated Friday

Editors’ Notes Don’t call it easy listening; call it the lighter side of pop. Spanning hits from the ’70s to now, these are the songs that remind you that life can be relaxing even in the middle of the daily bustle—a comfort you can take in stride. Our editors regularly update this playlist. If you like a tune, add it to your library.
